doc.previous: The second floor of the Passenger Terminal Building is used for domestic departures and arrivals All ticketing boarding and baggage claim are handled on the second floor International arrivals go to immigration and baggage claim on the first floor International departures are ticketed on the fourth floor and board from the third floor
